name: Guineapigvmb
tagline: Included are all the files to repeat the analysis from "Chlamydia caviae infection alters abundance but not composition of the guinea pig vaginal microbiota" .
body:
### Welcome to the Guineapigvmb GitHub Pages.
Here you can find all kinds of R-code and data files to confirm our analysis of the healthy and C. caviae infected guinea pig vaginal microbiota and use in your own research:

### Readme 
The readme only includes the list of the main scripts. More detailed to come. Also if you need more infomation or help please contact me (Elizabeth Neuendorf) at eneuendorf@som.umaryland.edu or Pawel Gajer pgajer@gmail.com. 


### Support or Contact
